Welcome to AutoPlate.net!

We hope to make AutoPlate your source for Custom Printed License Plates and Frames. The AutoPlate product line is sold exclusively through advertising specialty distributors. This website was created for viewing by distributors and their prospective customers.

Screen Printed License Plates

Available in White Aluminum and 4 Hi-Gloss Polyethylene thicknesses for spot color applications.

Digitally Printed License Plates

Available in White Aluminum or 3 Polyethylene thicknesses with our unique Screened Hi-Gloss Clear Coat for the look of a Full Color glossy photo!

Raised Letter Frames

Black, Red, Blue, or Gray polystyrene with White, Red, Blue, Yellow, Metallic Silver, Metallic Gold, or Chrome hot stamped imprint.

Chrome Faced Frames

Black, Red, or Blue polystyrene frames with the face hot stamped in Standard or Premium Bright Chrome, Metallic Silver, or Metallic Gold. Copy is recessed or raised in recessed panels.

PolyCard License Plates

.024” PolyCard with Screen Printed imprint.

Motorcycle Plates

Available in .035” or .023” Hi-Gloss Polyethylene and PolyCard with Screen Printed imprint.
